WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.271
Email is your written record. It is the right channel when the customer

00:00:04.321 --> 00:00:08.592
needs documentation — an estimate, a technical summary, attachments they can reference later.

00:00:08.642 --> 00:00:12.914
It is also the slowest, so it is the wrong channel for anything

00:00:12.964 --> 00:00:13.364
urgent.
